      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "EVEN SHARPER (2) doesn't win out of turn, scoring just three times from 38 starts. Again tasted defeat last start when fourth over 1600m at this track, beaten 3.5 lengths. Nicely placed to figure in the outcome. HELL OF A GENT (4) drifted well back last start before winding up strongly to finish third, beaten 1.2 lengths, over 1200m at this track. Should run on into the finish again. THE BIG FREEZE (1) turned in a fine effort to score by a long neck at today's track and distance last time out to continue his outstanding recent form. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run. OKESUTORA (3) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start over 1600m at this track, beaten 3.5 lengths into fifth. Best efforts measure up so worth another chance. NASHA (8) can go one better without surprising.",
